cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new hierarchical rule-based model for classification tasks and a novel neural network architecture to efficiently learn the non-differentiable model. This work involves machine learning, artificial intelligence, and natural language processing, which are all covered by the arXiv CS sub-categories of cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR, and cs.NE. Among these, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories as they are directly related to the proposed model and architecture.
